title: Spacious three bedroom with deck!
posting_body: ['This lower level duplex is quite spacious with three bedrooms, one bath and a living room, dining room and front entrance room that can be used for just about anything!', 'This apartment is being turned during the month of august with fresh paint, a lovely neutral grey color!', 'Will be available Sept 1st!', 'You have your very own private deck off the front door and a storage area in the basement.', 'Shared coin op washer/ dryer is located in the basement.', 'The back yard is NOT fully fenced in, however dogs and cats are allowed at this property.', 'Pet deposit : $300', 'Cat monthly fee: 20$ Per animal, 2 max', 'Dog monthly fee 30$ Per animal, 2 max 40 lb max per dog.', 'There is ONE front parking space designated for this apartment.', 'Street parking for others.', 'No smoking', 'Looking for quiet respectful residents!', 'We pay water , trash, sewer and lawn care.', 'You pay electric and gas and internet.', 'Rent: 1800', 'Security deposit 1800', 'First month rent and security deposit due at lease signing.', 'Looking for total income to be 2.5/3xs rent', 'Managed and owned by local family.', 'No giant management company!', 'Please email to set up a showing.']
